quran[339]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Sano aŵala ŵangakwembecheya yakusimangana Nowe ni akuti: “Ligongo chichi ngatutuluchila malaika (kuti gaŵe mitume kukwetu), kapena tum’bone M’mbuje gwetu (juchitendelaga umboni ya utume wa Muhammadi ﷺ)?” Chisimu pamasile paalikwesyisye m’mitima mwao, ni anyosisye kunyosya kwekulungwa"
  25,22,"Lisiku lyatachigaona malaika kuchiŵa kwangali kusengwa lyele lisikulyo kwaakuleŵa, ni gachiŵecheta (malaikago kuti): “Kuŵele kwakusiŵilidwa kusyene (kwa jenumanja lelo kupata yambone).”"
  25,23,Ni tuuchiiŵichilila itendo (yambone) yaŵapanganyisye ni tuuchiitenda kuŵa luwundu lwakuwululusyidwa
  25,24,Ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo lyele lisikulyo tachikola malo gambone nnope gakutamilichika ni malo gambone nnope gagusama
  25,25,"Soni (kumbuchilani) lisiku lyalichipapuka liwunde ni kutendekasya lipundugulu, nambo soni achimalaika ni kutulusyidwa mwawinji"
  25,26,"Uchimwene wakuonaonape lyele lisikulyo uchiŵa wa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ni lichiŵa lisiku lyakusausya nnope kwa achimakafili"
  25,27,"Soni (kumbuchilani) lisiku lyatachililuma jwalupuso magasa gakwe ganagaŵili achitiji: “E nkongwene! Ningajigale litala imo ni Ntenga ﷺ.”"
  25,28,“Ah kutapana kwangune! Nabolaga nga nganinantenda jwantijwanti kuŵa nsyoŵe.”
  25,29,"“Chisimu pamasile paasochelesye une kwakuleka Chikumbusyo (Qur’an) panyuma pakumbichilila, soni shetani aŵele jwakunneka mundu (ngankamuchisya pa ipotesi).”"
  25,30,"Sano Ntenga ﷺ ni jwatite: “E Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu ŵandu ŵangu ajitesile aji Qur’an kuŵa chindu chakulechedwa (pangajisooma ni ngakuuya malamusi gakwe).”"
  25,31,"Soni iyyoyopeyo twam’bichile ntume jwalijose m’magongo kuumila mwa akuleŵa, sano Ambuje ŵenu akukwanila kuŵa Nkongola nambo soni Nkukamuchisya"
  25,32,"Soni aŵala ŵaakanile ni akutiji: “Ligongo chichi Qur’an nganijintuluchila jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) mwanakamo?” Iyyoyopeyo (tukujitulusya panandipanandi) kuti tuulimbanganye najo ntima wenu, ni tujitulwisye (kukwenu) mwakosoŵalila (pakujitulusya mwambolembole mu ipande yepanje chenene)"
  25,33,"Soni ŵanganyao nganaŵa ayiche nacho kukwenu chitagu chilichose (chakumpinga nacho), ikaŵeje Uwwe chituŵiche nacho kukwenu chakuona (chakwanga chitagucho), ni kagopolanye kakwe kambone"
  25,34,"Aŵala ŵatachisonganganyisidwa (alinkuutidwa) chamakuku wa ku Jahannama, ŵanganyao ni ŵatachiŵa pamalo pakusakala nnope, nambo soni ni ŵakusokonechela nnope kwitala (lyagoloka)"
  25,35,"Soni chisimu pamasile patwampele Musa Chitabu (Taurat), ni twam’bichile nkulugwe Haruna kuŵa nkunkamuchisya"
  25,36,"Ni twatite: “Jawulani ŵanaŵaŵilimmwe ku ŵandu aŵala ŵaayikaaniile isimosimo Yetu.” Basi ni twajonasile kusyene (panyuma pakwakanila achimitengao)"
  25,37,"Nombe nao ŵandu ŵa Nuhu; ndema jaŵaakaaniile achimitenga, twamisisye (ni chigumula), ni twatesile kuŵa chilosyo kwa ŵandu. Sano ŵalupuso twalinganyichisye ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope"
  25,38,"Nambo soni achina Adi, achina Samuda, achimisyene chisima kwisa soni mikutula jejinji ja chilikati chao"
  25,39,"Soni jwalijose (mwa ŵanganyao), twampele ilandanyo (kuŵa maumboni ni ijiiganyo), soni ŵaliose (mwa ŵanganyao) twajonasile kusyene (panyuma pakwakanila achimitenga ŵao)"
  25,40,"Soni chisimu ŵanganyao (achimakafili ŵa pa Maaka m’maulendo gao gakuja ku Shami), akasaupitaga musi (wa Sodomu) awula wana kumputilaga ula jakusakala (jamaganga), ana ngaakasaŵaga ali nkuuona? Nambo kuti akuŵaga akakwembecheya yakwimuka m’malembe, (niligongo lyakwe ngaakukulupililaga)"
  25,41,"Soni ndema jaakum’bona mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ngaakuntenda inepe ikaŵeje chipongwe (pakuŵecheta kuti): “Ana aju ni jwantumisye Allah kuŵa ntenga?”"
  25,42,"“Jwaasigele panandi kuti atusochelesye kuleka milungu jetu, ingaŵaga kuti twapililile pa jalakwejo.” Sano ŵanganyao tachiika kumanyilila ndema jatachiiona ilagasyo kuti nduni jwakusokonechela nnope kwitala (lyagoloka)"
  25,43,Ana mum’bweni ajula jwaachitesile chisako chakwe kuŵa nnungu jwakwe? Ana mmwe ni mpaka mbe nkun’gosa jwakwe (kuti jukakuya isako yakwe)
  25,44,"Kapena nkuganichisya yanti ŵanganyao akupikana kapena kuitaga mulunda (yankwasalila)? Nganaŵatu ŵanganyao ikaŵeje ali mpela inyama yakulanga, nambo soni ŵanganyao ni ŵasokonechele nnope kwitala (lyagoloka kuipunda inyama yakulanga)"
  25,45,"Ana nganimwaona Ambuje ŵenu yatite pakutambasya m’bulili (kutandila kutiŵila mpaka kopoka kwa lyuŵa)? Angasache angautesile kuŵa wakutamilichika (wangasukuna, ni kukaliji chilope kwangali muusi). Soni tulitesile lyuŵa kuŵa nkuulondolela (m’bulilio, panyuma pakopoka lyuŵa m’bulili ukasatanda kwipipa)"
  25,46,Kaneko ni tukasauwumbataga Kukwetu kuwumbata kwa panandipanandi (mpaka ukasamalaga lyuŵa lili liyiche pewuwo)
  25,47,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwam’biichiile ŵanganyammwe chilo kuŵa chiwaalo (pakusiŵilila ilu yenu ni chipi chakwe), soni (ni am’biichiile) lugono kuŵa kupumula (kwa ilu yenu), ni awuŵisile muusi kuŵa ndema jakubalalikangana (kupita nchisosa lisiki)"
  25,48,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaakasatumisyaga mbungo kuŵa chisengwasyo paujo pa ukoto Wakwe (wula nkanijigwe), ni tukasatulusya kuumila kwinani mesi gakulenjela"
  25,49,"Kuti ni galakwego tusyuchisye chilambo chachiwe, ni tumwechesye ine (mu iwumbe) yatwaigumbile (mpela) ilango kwisa soni ŵandu ŵajinji"
  25,50,"Soni chisimu Uwwe tukujigaŵanyaga (wulajo) chilikati chao kuti aŵeje ŵakumbuchila (ukoto Wetu), nambo ŵandu ŵajinji akukana (chikulupi) ikaŵeje ukafili (basi)"
  25,51,Soni tungasache tungatumisye m’musi uliose nkutetela (jwaojwaope)
  25,52,"Basi ngasimwajitika achimakafili (pa isako yao), nambo n’dimbane nao nijele (Qur’aniji) kulimbana kwekulungwa"
  25,53,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaasisimangenye mbwani siŵili, aji jamesi gakunon’ga gakumasya njota, najiji jamesi gachijete gakuŵaŵa. Ni juŵisile chilikati chakwecho uŵigo, ni chilekanganyo chakulekanganya kusyene"
  25,54,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaagumbile mundu kuumila m’mesi, ni am’biichiile ulongo ŵakupagwana ni waulombela. Soni Ambuje ŵenu aŵele Ŵakombola kusyene"
  25,55,Soni ŵanganyao (achimakafili) akuŵa ali nkuchigalagatila chinepe changaŵaga Allah changaŵa nkwakamuchisya (naga ali achigalagatile) kapena kwapa ilagasyo (naga ali nganachigalagatila). Sano kafili ni akuŵaga nkunkamuchisya (shetani) pa (kwapitikuchila) Ambujegwe
  25,56,Ni nganituntumisya mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ikaŵeje kuti m’be nkutagulila abali jakusengwasya nambo soni nkutetela
  25,57,"Jilani: “Une ngangun’juga malipilo galigose pa yalakwe (yakulungusya utengayi), nambo jwasachile kujigala litala lyakuja kwa M’mbujegwe (pakutola chipanje chakwe basi ngangunkanya).”"
  25,58,"Soni jegamilani kwa (Allah) Jwaumi wandamo, Ajula jwaali Jwangawa, ni nluswejesyeje Lumbili Lwakwe. Soni jukwanile Jwalakwe pa sambi sya achikapolo Ŵakwe kuŵa Jwaasimanya chenene"
  25,59,"Ajula juŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka ni yaili chilikati chakwe m’moŵa nsano nalimo, kaneka nijwatenjele pa Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu). Jwaukoto wejinji, basi mum’busyani ya Jwalakwe nkumanyilila chenene (yambili Syakwe)"
  25,60,"Soni naga ali asalilidwe (yanti): “Munsujudilani Jwaukoto wejinji.” Akasatiji: “Ana Jwaukoto wejinji ninduni? Ana tunsujudile jwankutuchisya mmwe?” Sano (gele maloŵega) gaajonjechesye ŵanganyao kutalikangana (ni yakuona)"
  25,61,"Anyakwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) Ajula (Allah) jwaŵisile kwinani ndondwa syekulungwa-kulungwa ni mwakwenda mwakwe, ni aŵisile soni kwalakweko nyali (lyuŵa) kwisa soni mwesi wakumulika"
  25,62,Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaŵisile chilo ni muusi kuŵa yaakuyaana ni kuchengana-chengana kwa jwaakusaka kumbuchila kapena kusaka kutogolela
  25,63,"Sano achikapolo ŵa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji ni aŵala ŵaakwenda pachilambo mwakulinandiya, nambo soni ajinga ali aŵechete kukwao (maloŵe gangalumbana), akasajangaga ni maloŵe gantima tusya"
  25,64,Ni aŵala ŵaakupitisyaga ndaŵi ja chilo achin’galagatilaga M’mbuje gwao mwakusujudu ni kwima (kuswali)
  25,65,"Ni aŵala ŵaakutiji: “Ambuje ŵetu! Tutyochesyani ilagasyo ya Jahannama, chisimu ilagasyo yakwe iŵele yangalekangana nayo.”"
  25,66,“Chisimu jalakwe (Jahannama) gaŵele malo gakusakala nnope kutamilichika ni kwimilichika.”
  25,67,"Ni aŵala ŵati achitolaga ngakasamisangaga soni ŵangatenda ugagadi, nambo akasaŵa ŵakwimilichika chilikati cha yalakweyo"
  25,68,"Ni aŵala ŵangaakum’bendaga nnungu jwine pampepe ni Allah, soni ni ngaakuwulagaga mundu jwaakanyisye Allah (kum’bulaga) ikaŵeje paligongo lyakwitichika (ni malamusi ga Dini), nambo soni ŵangatenda chikululu. Sano jwachatende yele nikuti chasimangane ni ilagasyo (ya pa duniya)"
  25,69,"Ilagasyo tiikajonjechesyedwe kukwakwe lisiku lya Kiyama, ni chijukalonjele mwalakwemo aku juli jwakunyosyedwa"
  25,70,"Ikaŵeje ŵatesile toba, ni kulupilila, ni kupanganyaga masengo gambone; basi ŵanganyao Allah chakatindanichisye yakusakala yao ni yambone, soni Allah aŵele Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  25,71,"Sano jwaakutenda toba ni kupanganyaga yambone, nikuti chisimu jwalakwejo jukulamba kwa Allah pakutenda toba jisyesyene"
  25,72,"Ni aŵala ŵangatendela umboni yaunami, nambo soni naga achipitaga malo ga yachanache akasapitaga mwa adabu (ja kuitundumalila yalakweyo)"
  25,73,Ni aŵala ŵaakutiji naga ali akumbusyidwe ni ma Ȃya ga M’mbuje gwao ŵangagagwila mwa usiiwa ni ungalola
  25,74,"Ni aŵala ŵaakutiji: “Ambuje ŵetu! Tupani kuumila mu achiŵammakwetu ni ŵanache ŵetu chakuteteŵachisya meso, ni ntutende uwwe kuŵa achinnongola ŵa ŵandu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah).”"
  25,75,"Ŵanganyao takalipidwe yumba yapenani (ku Mbepo), ni takasimangane nao mwalakwemo uchimbichimbi ni ntendele"
  25,76,Takaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo – Kaje kusalala malo gakutamilichika ni kwimilichika gakwe
  25,77,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ambuje ŵangu nga nganankochesyaga ŵanganyammwe kungaŵaga kuomba kwenu (kwankum’bombaga naga ili impatile ipato). Nambo sano ni pamasile pamunkanile (Jwalakwe). Basi sano (ipotesi) ni tiiŵe yangalekangana nayo ndema ni katema"
  26,1,Twâ-Sîn-Mîm
  26,2,Aga ni ma Ȃya ga m’Chitabu chakusalichisya
  26,3,Mwinetu mmwe kuŵa nkulijonanga mwasyene (ni madandausi) ligongo lyanti ŵanganyao ngakuŵa ŵakulupilila
  26,4,"Tungasache tungatuluchisye ŵanganyao kuumila kwinani chisimosimo, basi ngosi syao ni sikaliji syakuteteŵalila kuchalakwecho (mwanti akaujitiche Usilamu mwakanganisyidwa, nambo ngatukusasaka kwakanganichisya ŵandu ku Usilamu)"
  26,5,"Ni ngachikwaichililaga chikumbusyo chasambano chakuumila kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ikaŵeje akasaŵaga ŵanganyao ŵaachitundumalila chalakwecho"
  26,6,"Sano pamasile pakanile, basi sampano tisyaichilile abali sya ayila yaaŵele ali nkuitendela chipongwe"
  26,7,Ana nganaliona litaka – kuti mmela ulingwa watuumesisye mwalakwemo wa ntundu uliose wakusalala chenene
  26,8,"Chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana chilosyo (cha ukombosi wa Allah), nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,9,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu, ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,10,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kaŵam’bilasile Ambuje ŵenu Musa (ni kuntenda kuti): “Jaulani ku ŵandu ŵalupuso.”"
  26,11,“Ŵandu ŵa Firiauna; ana ngakogopa?”
  26,12,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu une ngogopa kuti chakanganile.”"
  26,13,"“Ni chikaŵanikwe chidali changu (ligongo lyakunganila), nambo soni lulimi lwangu ngalukuchachukaga chenene, basi tumisyani (soni utengau) kwa Haruna (kuti akangamusyeje).”"
  26,14,"“Soni ŵanganyao akwete magambo ganaleŵele, ni ngogopa kuti takambulaje.”"
  26,15,"(Allah) jwatite: “Ngwamba! Basi jaulani ŵanaŵaŵilimmwe ni isimosimo Yetu. Chisimu Uwwe chitukaŵe namwe imo (pakunkamuchisya) aku tuchipikanilaga (yatakaŵecheteje).”"
  26,16,"“Basi mun’jaulilani Firiauna ni kuja kuti: ‘Chisimu uwwe (jwalijose mwetuwe) ntenga jwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosospe.’"
  26,17,‘(Tutumidwe) kuti mwaleche tuŵigule nao ŵanache ŵa Israila (tujauleje nao ku Shami).”
  26,18,"(Firiauna) jwatite (kwa Musa): “Ana nganitunnela kukwetu n’di mwanache, soni ni kutama nowe pa umi wenu yaka yejinji?”"
  26,19,“Ni mwatesile chitendo chenu chamwatesile chila (chakuwulaga mundu) aku n’di ŵakanila (ukoto wangu kukwenu).”
  26,20,"(Musa) jwatite: “Natesile yalakweyo pajele ndemajo kutendaga une ndili jumpepe mwa ŵangamanyilila (yakwayana ni Ambuje ŵangu ni Utume).”"
  26,21,"“Basi ni nantisile ŵanganyammwe ndema janan’jogwepe, basi Ambuje ŵangu ni ambele lunda lwaulamusi, soni ni andesile kuŵa mwa achimitenga.”"
  26,22,“Ana soni weleu ni ukoto wakungumba nao kutendaga mwaŵisile mu ukapolo ŵanache ŵa Israila!”
  26,23,"Firiauna jwatite: “Ana M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosopejo ni nduni?”"
  26,24,"(Musa) jwatite: “M’mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, nam’baga jenumanja nkwete ntima wakusaka kusimichisya (tinsimichisye yele).”"
  26,25,"(Firiauna) jwasalile ŵaŵaliji mungulugulu mwakwe (mwachalu) kuti: “Ana ngankupikana (yawanache yajukuŵechetayi)?”"
  26,26,"(Musa) jwatite: “M’mbuje gwenu jenumanja nambo soni M’mbuje jwa achatati ŵenu ŵandanda.”"
  26,27,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Chisimu ntenga jwenu jwatumisyidwe kukwenuju jwamasoka.”"
  26,28,"(Musa) jwatite: “M’mbuje jwa kungopoko ni kungapililo ni yaili chilikati chakwe, nam’baga jenumanja ŵana lunda (timmanyilile yele).”"
  26,29,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Naga nkulitendela nnungu jwinepe jwangaŵaga une, chisimu chene chinantende kuŵa jumpepe mwa akutaŵidwa.”"
  26,30,"(Musa) jwatite: “Atamose ndili nam’bichilile nacho chindu chakuonechela palangulangu?”"
  26,31,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Ŵikani nacho, naga n’di mwa akuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  26,32,Basi (Musa) ni jwaponyisye simbo jakwe (pasi). Naalole! Jasyuchile lijoka lyakuonechela
  26,33,Soni ni jwakopwesye ligasa lyakwe. Naalole! Lyasyuchile lyeswela (lyakumelemenda) kwa akulola
  26,34,"(Firiauna) jwasalile achinkulungwa ŵaŵaliji mungulugulu mwakwe kuti: “Chisimu jwalakweju nsaŵi jwakumanyilila nnope (usaŵi).”"
  26,35,"“Jukusaka kuti junkopokasye m’chilambo mwenu ni usaŵi wakweo, ana ni tinnamule yantiuli?”"
  26,36,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite (pakwapanga lunda Afiriauna): “Munnechelesyani panandi jwalakwe ni nkulugwejo (nkaawulaga chitema) ni ntumisye m’misinda akusonganganya.”"
  26,37,“Kuti ayiche najo kukwenu nsaŵi jwalijose jwali jwakumanyilila nnope (usaŵi).”
  26,38,Basi asaŵi ni ŵasonganganyisidwe pa ndema jisyesyene ja lisiku lyakumanyika
  26,39,"Ŵandu nombe ni ŵawusyidwe kuti: “Ana jenumanja tinsongangane?”"
  26,40,“Kuti mwine uwwejo twakuye asaŵi naga ŵanganyao aŵe ŵakupunda.”
  26,41,"Basi ndema jaŵaiche asaŵi ŵatite kwa Firiauna: “Ana chisimu kukwetu chikuŵe kwana malipilo (gambone) natuŵaga uwwejo ni ŵakupunda?”"
  26,42,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Elo, konjechesya soni pelepo chisimu ŵanganyammwe pajele ndemajo chim’be mwa akuŵandichisyidwa (kukwangu).”"
  26,43,"Musa jwasalile ŵanganyao kuti: “Ponyani jenumanja yankusaka kuponyayo.”"
  26,44,"Basi ni ŵaponyisye ngonji syao ni simbo syao, niŵatite: “Kwa machili ga Firiauna chisimu uwwe ni ŵachituŵe ŵakupunda.”"
  26,45,Sano Musa ni jwaponyisye simbo jakwe. Naalole! Jalakwe jamisile mwanakamo yaunami yaŵaliji nkulosya
  26,46,Basi asaŵi ŵasenjelemukwiche kusujudu
  26,47,"Ŵatite: “Tunkulupilile M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,48,“M’mbuje jwa Musa ni Haruna.”
  26,49,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Munkulupilile jwalakweju une nkaninampe lusa? Chisimu jwalakweju ni jwankulungwa jwenu jwan’jiganyisye usaŵi. Basi chisimu pangakaŵapa chiyyimanye (yachinantende). Chisimu chingate makono genu ni ngongolo syenu mwakutindanya (ligasa lyakun'dyo ni likau lyakunchiji, kapena ligasa lyakunchiji ni likau lyakun'dyo), kaneka ni chinankomele pansalaba ŵanaose.”"
  26,50,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Yangali kandu, chisimu uwwe kwa M’mbuje gwetu tukuujila.”"
  26,51,"“Chisimu uwwe tukwete chikulupi chanti, M’mbuje gwetu jutukululuchile sambi syetu ligongo lyakuŵa ŵandanda mwa akukulupilila.”"
  26,52,"Ni twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Ŵigulani lwachilo ni achikapolo Ŵangu, chisimu ŵanganyammwe tinkuuyidwe.”"
  26,53,Basi Firiauna ni jwatumisye m’misinda (josope) akusonganganya
  26,54,"(Ŵaŵapitaga nchigombelesya yanti): “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (ŵanache ŵa Israila) ali kwene kankutula kannono.”"
  26,55,“Soni chisimu ŵanganyao akutupikasya ntima.”
  26,56,“Soni chisimu uwwe tuli wosope (ŵajinji nambo soni) tuli mesope (tukwalolechesya ŵanganyao kuti akatupatisya ipato iliyose).”
  26,57,Basi Uwwe ni twakopwesye ŵanganyao (ŵanya Afiriauna) m’matimbe ni achitutumule
  26,58,Kwisa soni mu imatiilo yachipanje ni m’malo mwakuchimbichika
  26,59,"Mwele (ni mutwatendele), ni twaitesile kuŵa yawinjilwa ni ŵanache ŵa Israila"
  26,60,Basi ŵanganyao ni ŵakuyiye (ŵanache ŵa Israilao) pakopoka kwa lyuŵa
  26,61,"Basi ndema jagaonegene makuga ganagaŵili (likuga lya Firiauna ni lya Musa), ŵandu ŵa Musa ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe chitukamulwe.”"
  26,62,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ngwamba! Chisimu Ambuje ŵangu ali none, chanjongolele (yakutenda kuti mpaka tujokoche).”"
  26,63,"Basi ni twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Putani mbwani ni simbo jenujo.” Ni jagaŵanyiche, upande uliose waliji nti chisawu litumbi lyekulungwa"
  26,64,Ni twaŵandichisye palakwepo ŵaneo (Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe)
  26,65,Ni twan’jokwele Musa ni ŵaŵaliji najo imo wosopeŵene
  26,66,Kaneka ni twamisisye ŵaneo (Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe)
  26,67,Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chimanyisyo (cha ukombosi wa Allah). Nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila
  26,68,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu niŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,69,Soni mwasoomelani ŵanganyao abali ja Ibrahima
  26,70,"Pandema jajwawusisye babagwe ni ŵandu ŵakwe kuti: “Chichi nkuchigalagatila?”"
  26,71,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Tukugalagatila isanamu, basi ni tukwendelechela kuigalagatila ndema ni katema.”"
  26,72,"(Ibrahima) jwatite: “Ana akasampikanaga pati nchaŵilangaga?”"
  26,73,“Kapena akasampaga chikamuchisyo (pati nchagalagatilaga) kapena kupeleka masausyo (naga ngaagalagatila)?”
  26,74,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “(Ngwamba,) Nambo twasimene achatati ŵetu achitendaga mwatukutendelamu.”"
  26,75,"(Ibrahima) jwatite: “Ana nkwaona aŵa ŵam’bele n’di nkwagalagatila,”"
  26,76,“Jenumanja ni achatati ŵenu ŵaŵalongolele?”
  26,77,"“Basi chisimu ŵanganyao ni amagongo ŵangu, ikaŵeje M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,78,"“Ajula juŵangumbile, nambo soni Jwalakwe ni jwaakunjongolela (kwitala lyagoloka).”"
  26,79,“Nambo soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaakundisyaga ni kumwesya.”
  26,80,“Soni pati nwasile basi Jwalakwe ni jwaakumbosyaga.”
  26,81,"“Nambo soni Ajula jwatambe chiwa, nikwisa kumba umi soni (ku Kiyama).”"
  26,82,“Nambo soni Ajula jwangukolela tama janti tachingululuchila ileŵi yangu Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  26,83,"“Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbani lunda lwakwilanyichisya (ichindu), ni musimanganye ni ŵandu ŵambone.”"
  26,84,“Soni mumbani kusaalidwa kwambone m’mikutula jamunyuma.”
  26,85,“Ni mundende kuŵa mwa akujitawala Mbepo Jachindimba.”
  26,86,"“Ni mwakululuchile atati ŵangu, chisimu ŵalakweo aŵele ŵampepe mwa akusokonechela.”"
  26,87,“Soni nkaja kunjalusya pa Lisiku lyatachijimusyidwaga ŵandu m’malembe.”
  26,88,"“Lisiku lyangakamuchisya chipanje namuno ŵanache,”"
  26,89,“Ikaŵeje jwatachiika kwa Allah ni ntima weswela.”
  26,90,Ni jichiŵandichisyidwa Mbepo kwa ŵakun’jogopa (Allah)
  26,91,Ni uchionesyedwa Moto Waukali kwa ŵapombotale
  26,92,"Ni kuchiŵechetedwa kukwao: “Ali kwapi aŵala ŵamwaliji nkwagalagatila,”"
  26,93,“Kunneka Allah? Ana mpaka akombole kunkamuchisya ŵanganyammwe kapena kulikamuchisya achimisyene?”
  26,94,Basi ni tachiponyedwa chamakuku mwalakwemo ŵanganyao ni akupombotala (ŵane)
  26,95,Kwisa soni asilikali ŵa Ibulisu wosopeŵene
  26,96,"Tachiti, aku ŵanganyao achikanganaga mwalakwemo"
  26,97,“Tukunnumbila Allah! Chisimu uwwe twaliji nkusokonechela kwakuonechela.”
  26,98,“Pandema jatwannandanyaga ŵanganyammwe ni M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”
  26,99,“Ni nganatusokonesya ikaŵeje akuleŵa.”
  26,100,“Ni nganitukola akutuombola.”
  26,101,“Namuno nsyoŵe jwapantima (jwanti ni kutukamuchisya.)”
  26,102,"“Mwanti tungakole upile wakuujila (ku duniya), basi tungajiile kuŵa mwa akukulupilila.”"
  26,103,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,104,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,105,Ŵandu ŵa Nuhu ŵaakaaniile achimitenga
  26,106,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Nuhu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,107,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,108,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,109,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵatu malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,110,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,111,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ana tunkulupilile mmwe kutendaga ŵaakunkuya ni ŵandu ŵapasi?”"
  26,112,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana umanyilisichi ungwete pa yaŵaliji nkutenda ŵanganyao?”"
  26,113,"“Nganichiŵatu chiŵalanjilo chao ikaŵeje kwa Ambuje ŵangu, ingaŵe mwamanyililaga.”"
  26,114,“Soni nganimba une jwanti ni kwaŵinga ŵakulupilila.”
  26,115,“Nganimba une ikaŵeje nkutetela jwakuonechela.”
  26,116,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Naga ngankuleka E mmwe Nuhu! Chisimu chene chim’be mwa akusomedwa maganga.”"
  26,117,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu ŵandu ŵangu angaaniile.”"
  26,118,"“Basi jilanyani chilikati changune ni ŵanganyao ni chilanyo (chambone), ni munjokole une ni ŵandu ŵali none mu ŵakulupilila.”"
  26,119,Basi ni twan’jokwele jwalakwe pamo ni ŵaŵaliji najo m’chombo chepachile
  26,120,Kaneko ni twamisisye ŵakusigalao panyuma pakwe
  26,121,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,122,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,123,Achina Adi ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,124,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Hudu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,125,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,126,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,127,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵatu malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,128,“Ana nkutaŵa pachikwesya palipose pakusalala nyumba syeleuleu mwamasanje (pagamba kusaka kulosya machili ngaŵa syagonamo)?”
  26,129,“Ni nkulitaŵila makome gamakulungwakulungwa nti chisawu tinnonjele?”
  26,130,“Soni ntite mpute ngondo nkasaputa mwakulikwesya.”
  26,131,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,132,“Soni mun’jogopani Ajula jwampele ichindu (yambonembone) yankuimanyilila.”
  26,133,“Ampele ilango ni ŵanache.”
  26,134,“Kwisa soni migunda ni sulo syatutumule.”
  26,135,“Chisimu une ngun’jogopela ŵanganyammwe ilagasyo ya lisiku lyekulungwa.”
  26,136,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Yalumope kukwetu, n’jamuche kapena nkaŵa mwa akwamuka.”"
  26,137,“Nganiyiŵatu ayi (yatukutendayi) ikaŵeje nyendele ja ŵandu ŵandanda.”
  26,138,“Soni nganituŵatu uwwe ŵanti ni kupedwa ilagasyo.”
  26,139,"Basi ŵankaaniile, ni twajonasile. Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,140,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,141,Achina Samuda ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,142,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Swaleh kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,143,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,144,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,145,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵa malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,146,“Ana (nkuganichisya kuti) tin’gambe kulechedwa mwantunjelele pa yaili pepanoyi.”
  26,147,"“M’migunda ni sulo syatutumule,”"
  26,148,“Ni mmela kwisa soni mitende itungatunga yakwe yakutependala?”
  26,149,“Soni nkusepa m’matumbi majumba mwa ufundi.”
  26,150,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,151,“Ni ngasimpikanila chilamusi cha akupunda malile (pasambi).”
  26,152,"“Aŵala ŵaakuwatanganya pa chilambo, soni ŵangajilanya.”"
  26,153,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Chisimu mmwe n’di mwa akulojedwa.”"
  26,154,"“Nganim’ba mmwe ikaŵeje mundu mpela uwwewe, basi ikani nacho chisimosimo naga n’di mwa akuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  26,155,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Aji ngamiya jajikongwe; jikwete kumwa (mesi), nombe jenumanja nkwete kumwa (mesi) palisiku lyakumanyika (ngamiya lisiku lyakwe nombe jenumanja lisiku lyenu).”"
  26,156,“Ni ngasin’jikwaya ni yakusakala iliyose itakwisa mwainkwembekenye ilagasyo yalisiku lyekulungwa.”
  26,157,"Nambo ŵanganyao ŵajisikite, mwanti ŵasyuchile kuŵa ŵakuligamba"
  26,158,"Basi ni yakwembekenye ilagasyo. Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,159,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,160,Ŵandu ŵa Lutwi ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,161,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Lutwi kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,162,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,163,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,164,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵa malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,165,"“Ana nkwaichilila achalume (achimijenu pakwatenda matanyula) mu iwumbe,”"
  26,166,“Ni nkwaleka aŵala ŵan’guumbiile Ambuje ŵenu kuti aŵeje achiŵammakwenu? Nambo jenumanja ni ŵandu ŵakusumba mpika.”
  26,167,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Naga ngankuleka (yakutukanya matanyula) mmwe Lutwi! Chisimu chene chim’be mwa akukoposyedwa.”"
  26,168,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chisimu une ni jumpepe mwa akuiŵenga mwaukali itendo yenu (yamatanyulai).”"
  26,169,“Ambuje ŵangu! Munjokolani une ni liŵasa lyangu ku yaakupanganya ŵanganyaŵa.”
  26,170,Ni twan’jokwele jwalakwe ni liŵasa lyakwe lyosopelyene
  26,171,Ikaŵeje kangalamba kachikongwe (ŵankwao Lutwi ŵaŵaliji) mwa akusigalila munyuma
  26,172,Kaneko ni twajonasile ŵaneo
  26,173,Ni twagwichisye ŵanganyao wula (jamaganga). Kaje kusakala wula ja akuteteledwa
  26,174,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,175,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,176,Achinsyene itekete (ŵandu ŵa ku Madiyana) ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,177,"Ndema jaŵasalile Shuaibu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,178,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,179,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,180,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵa malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,181,“Gumbasyani chipiimo chambale ni ngasim’ba mwa akupungusya.”
  26,182,“Ni mpimeje ni sikelo jakulungamika.”
  26,183,"“Soni ngasimwapunguchisyaga ŵandu indu yao, ni ngasin’jendagajendaga pa chilambo kupita nchiwatanganya.”"
  26,184,“Soni mun’jogopani Ajula juŵan’gumbile ŵanganyammwe kwisa soni mikutula ja ŵandu ŵandanda.”
  26,185,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Chisimu mmwe n’di mwa akulojedwa.”"
  26,186,“Soni nganim’ba mmwe ikaŵeje mundu mpela uwwewe. Soni uwwe tukun’ganichisya kwene kuti n’di jumpepe mwa ŵandu ŵaunami.”
  26,187,“Basi tugwichisyani uwwe chipande cha liwunde (kuti chitujonanje) nam’baga mmwejo n’di mwa akuŵecheta yakuona.”
  26,188,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu ni ŵaakumanyilila chenene yankupanganya.”"
  26,189,"Ni ŵankaaniile, basi ni yakwembekenye ilagasyo yalisiku lyam’bulili (waliwunde lyaipotesi), chisimu yalakweyo yaliji ilagasyo ya lisiku lyekulungwa"
  26,190,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,191,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,192,Soni chisimu jele (Qur’aniji) jiŵele jakutulusyidwa kuumila kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  26,193,Watulwiche najo Nsiimu (Jibulilu) wakulupichika
  26,194,"Pantima penu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), kuti m’be mwa akutetela"
  26,195,Mu chiŵecheto cha Charabu chakupikanika chenene
  26,196,Soni yalakweyi yili mu itabu ya (ŵandu) ŵandanda
  26,197,Ana nganichiŵa chilosyo kukwao chanti ŵalijiganye ŵa ŵanache ŵa Israila (mpela Abdullah bin Salâm ŵaŵaujitiche Usilamu) ni kujimanya jalakwe (Qur’aniji kuti jakuona)
  26,198,Soni tungajitulusye (Qur’aniji) kwa ŵanepe ŵangaŵa ŵarabu
  26,199,"Basi ni kujisooma kukwao, nga nganaŵa ŵakujikulupilila jalakwe"
  26,200,Iyyoyopeyo tukupitisye (kujikanila Qur’an) m’mitima mwa akuleŵa (atamose kuti jukwasoomela mwarabu n’jao)
  26,201,Ngaajikulupilila jalakwe mpaka akaiwone ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  26,202,Basi ni tiichaichilila mwachisupuchisya ŵanganyao akakumanyilila
  26,203,"Ni tachiti: “Ana uwwe ngakomboleka kupedwa lipesa (kuti tutende toba)?”"
  26,204,Ana akuijanguya ilagasyo Yetu
  26,205,"Ana nkuiona uli, naga tuli twasengwasisye ŵanganyao kwa yaka (yejinji)"
  26,206,Kaneka ni kwaichilila (ipotesi) yaŵaliji nkupedwa chilanga
  26,207,Ngasiyakamuchisya ayila yaŵele ali nkusengwasyidwa nayo
  26,208,Soni Uwwe nganituujonanjeje musi uliose ikaŵeje wakolaga akutetela
  26,209,"Kuŵa chikumbusyo, soni Uwwe nganituŵa ŵalupuso (pakwajonanga ŵandu nkanitwatetele)"
  26,210,Soni mashetani ngaŵa ni gagatulwisye jalakwe (Qur’aniji mwaakuŵechetela achimakafili)
  26,211,"Soni ngaikuŵajilwa kukwao, nambo soni nganaŵa akombwele (kujitulusya)"
  26,212,Chisimu ŵanganyao yakupikanila (Qur’an kumawunde jichitulukaga) asiŵiiliidwe
  26,213,"Basi ngasimunnumbanjila pampepe ni Allah nnungu jwine, ntakwika mum’bele mwa akulagasyidwa"
  26,214,Ni mwatetelani ŵalukosyo lwenu ŵali ŵakuŵandichila
  26,215,Nimwagoyechesye lipapiko lyenu (lya chanasa) aŵala ŵankuyiye mwa ŵakulupilila
  26,216,"Sano naga akunnyosya basi jilani: “Chisimu une mambalene nayo ichindu yankutenda.”"
  26,217,"Nin’jegamile kwa (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwachanasa channope"
  26,218,Ajula jwaakum’bona ndema jankwima (jikape kuswali patahajjudi)
  26,219,Ni kutenganyikatenganyika kwenu (pakuswali ipindi nsano) pamo ni akusujudu (akuswali ŵane)
  26,220,"Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  26,221,Ana nantagulile ŵanganyammwe jwagakuntuluchilaga mashetani
  26,222,"Gakuntuluchilaga jwalijose jwaunami wejinji, jwasambi nnope"
  26,223,Gakuponyaga yagapikene (kwinani kwaponyela achibimbi) nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ŵaunami
  26,224,Akwimba chilaanga ŵaliose akasaŵakuyaga ŵasokonechele
  26,225,Ana ngankuiona yanti ŵanganyao m’chiŵata chilichose (chamaloŵe) akuŵa nkupojola
  26,226,Soni kuti ŵanganyao akasaŵechetaga yangakutendaga
  26,227,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, ni kunkolangaga Allah kwejinji, ni kulikulupusya achimisyene panyuma pakutendeledwa lupuso (pakwajanga achimakafili ni ilaanga pa ilaanga yao yaakwimba yakwagamba Asilamu). Sano pangakaŵapa tamanyilile aŵala ŵatesile lupuso kwagalauchila kutagalauchile"
  27,1,Twâ-Sîn. Aga ni ma Ȃya ga Qur’an nambo soni (chiŵele) Chitabu chakusalichisya
  27,2,Chongolo nambo soni chisengwasyo kwa ŵakulupilila
  27,3,"Aŵala ŵaakwimikaga Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, soni ŵanganyao ya Akhera akasaŵa ŵakulupilila kusyesyene"
  27,4,Chisimu aŵala ŵangakukulupilila ya Akhera twasalalichisye itendo yao mwanti ŵanyao agamba kuŵa pupulipupuli (nkusokonechela mwao)
  27,5,"Ŵanganyao ni aŵala ŵaakwete kupata ilagasyo yakunyalaya (pa duniya pano), nambo soni ŵanganyao ku Akhera tachiŵa ŵakwasika kusyene"
  27,6,"Soni chisimu mmwejo (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkusoomesyedwa Qur’an kuumila kwa (Allah) Jwalunda lwakusokoka, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  27,7,"(Kumbuchilani) katema kajwalisalile Musa liŵasa lyakwe kuti: “Chisimu une nauweni moto. Chinam’bichilile najo abali kuumila ku walakweo, kapena chinam’bichilile nacho chisinga chamoto kuti jenumanja n’jote.”"
  27,8,"Basi ndema jajwauŵichilile jwaŵilanjidwe kuti: “Ajaliiwe jwali pamoto ni jwali mungulugulu mwakwe. Nambo soni aswejele Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  27,9,"“E mmwe Musa! Chisimu Jwalakwejotu ni Une Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka.”"
  27,10,"“Soni ponyani simbo jenu.” Basi ndema jajwajiweni jinankutenganyika nti chisawu lijoka, jwagalawiche kutila nambo soni nganijulola munyuma. (Allah jwatite): “E mmwe Musa! Nkajogopa. Chisimu Une Achimitenga ŵangajogopa Kukwangu.”"
  27,11,"“Nambo jwalitendele lupuso kaneko ni galausya (pakupanganya) yambone panyuma pa yakusakala basi (ngunkululuchilaga), chisimu Une ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope.”"
  27,12,"“Soni jinjisyani ligasa lyenu pa mitima pa kansu jenu chilikopoche lili lyeswela ngaŵaga mwaulwele. (Ilosyo iŵiliyi ili) mu ilosyo nsano nancheche. (Jaulani nayo) kwa Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe, chisimu ŵanganyao aŵele ŵandu ŵakunyosya.”"
  27,13,"Basi ndema jayaichilile isimosimo Yetu yakuloleka ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Awu ni usaŵi wakuonechela.”"
  27,14,Ni ŵaikaaniile (isimosimoyo) mwalupuso nambo soni mwakulikwesya kutendaga mitima jao jaikulupilile kusyesyene. Basi nnole mujaŵelele mbesi ja akuwatanganya
  27,15,"Soni chisimu chene pamasile patwampele Daudi ni Sulaimana umanyilisi. Ni ŵatite ŵanaŵaŵili: “Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah Ajula jwaatulongwesye uwwe (pakutupa ukoto) kwapunda ŵajinji mwa achikapolo Ŵakwe ŵakulupilila.”"
  27,16,"Sano Sulaimana jwatamile chitengu cha Daudi. Ni jwatite: “E jenumanja ŵandu! Uwwe tujiganyisyidwe chiŵecheto cha ijuni, ni tupedwile chindu chilichose. Chisimu walakweu ni ukoto wakuonechela.”"
  27,17,"Ni ŵasonganganyisyidwe kwa Sulaimana asilikali ŵakwe kuumila m’majini, ŵandu ni ijuni. Basi ni ŵaliji ali nkwaalidwa m’mikutulamikutula (pakajende kakwe)"
  27,18,"Kwikanila ndema jaŵaiche ŵanganyao pachiŵata chambamba, lupamba lwatite (pakusisalila mbamba sijakwe): “E jenumanja achimbamba! Jinjilani m’majumba mwenu atakwika mwan’diŵete Sulaimana ni asilikali ŵakwe kutendaga ŵanganyao akakumanyilila.”"
  27,19,"Basi ni jwamwetulile (Sulaimana) mwakusechelela ligongo lya maloŵe gakwe (ga lupamba). Ni jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbani machili ganti ngomboleje kutogolela ukoto Ŵenu wamumbele une ni achinangolo ŵangu, nambo soni napakomboleje kutenda yambone yampaka iyyinonyele. Ni munyinjisye une mwa ukoto Ŵenu mu achikapolo Ŵenu ŵambone.”"
  27,20,"Ni jwapite nchendela ijuni, basi ni jwatite: “Itite uli kukwangu mbona ngangujiona ngukuku, kapena jili mwa akusoŵa?”"
  27,21,"“Chisimu chene chinajilagasye ni ilagasyo yakandapala, kapena chingambe kujisikita, ikaŵeje jiiche nalyo ligongo lyakupikanika (lyajisoŵele).”"
  27,22,"Nambo (ngukuku) nganijitama ndema jelewu, basi (nijaiche kwa Sulaimana ni) jatite: “Naikopocheele yanganiyyikopochela mmwe, ni nam’bichilile kuumila ku Sabai ni abali jakuonaonape.”"
  27,23,"“Chisimu une naasimene ŵakongwe ali nkwalamulila (ŵandu ŵa ku Sabai), ni apedwile chindu chilichose (chakuŵajilwa kola nchimwene), nambo soni akwete chindanda (cha uchimwene) chekulungwa nnope.”"
  27,24,"“Nasimene ŵalakweo ni ŵandu ŵao alinkulisujudila lyuŵa kunneka Allah, soni shetani jwasalalichisye itendo yao, ni jwasiŵilile kwitala (lyagoloka), basi ŵanganyao ngakupata chongoko,”"
  27,25,"“Mwanti ngaakunsujudila Allah Ajula jwaakukoposyaga yakusisika ya kumawunde ni petaka, soni ni akuimanyilila yankusisa ni yankulosya.”"
  27,26,“Allah pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo. M’mbuje jwa Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu) Jekulungwa nnope.”
  27,27,"(Sulaimana) jwatite: “Chitulole naga nkuŵecheta yakuona kapena n’di mwa akulambusya.”"
  27,28,"“Jaulani ni baluwa janguji ni nkajiponye kukwao, kaneko ni nkaatundumalile (nkatame pakutalichila) ni nkalole mwachigakaŵele majibu gao.”"
  27,29,"(Nyakongwe) ŵatite: “E jenumanja achinduna! Chisimu une jiponyedwe kukwangu baluwa jakuchimbichika.”"
  27,30,"“Chisimu jalakwe jikuumila kwa Sulaimana, soni chisimu jalakwe (jikuti): “”"
  27,31,"“Ngasin’dikwesya kukwangu, nambo mumbichilile n’di Asilamu.”"
  27,32,"(Nyakongwe) ŵatite: “E jenumanja achinduna! Mumbangani yakujila pangani janguji, une nganimba namwile chilichose mpaka nkambichilile (ni kumba nganisyo syenu).”"
  27,33,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Uwwe ni achinsyene machili, nambo soni achinsyene kuputa ngondo mwaukali, nambo yosope ili kukwenu, basi nnole muchinnamulile.”"
  27,34,"(Nyakongwe) ŵatite: “Chisimu achiŵenye naga ali aujinjile musi, akasaujonangaga ni kwatenda ŵakuchimbichika mwa ŵandu ŵakwe kuŵa ŵakunyosyeka, mwele ni mwaakasatendela (ndema syose).”"
  27,35,"“Basi chisimu une chindumisye kukwao ntuuka, basi ninole kuti ana tisiuje nayo yantiuli ndumetume.”"
  27,36,"Basi ndema jasyaiche (ndumetume sila) kwa Sulaimana, jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana nkungamuchisya ni chipanje? Yambele une Allah ili yambone nnope kupunda yampele ŵanganyammwe, nambo kuti jenumanja nkuchina ni ntuuka wenu.”"
  27,37,"(Kaneka Sulaimana ŵansalile nnongola jwa ndumetume kuti): “Ujilani kukwao, basi chisimu chene chitwaichilile ni asilikali ŵangaŵa nkombola ŵanganyao kulimbana nao, soni chisimu chene chitwakoposye ŵanganyao mwalakwemo ali ŵakunyosyeka, nambo soni ali atengwiche.”"
  27,38,"(Sulaimana) jwatite: “E jenumanja achinduna! Nduni mwa jenumanja jwataichenacho kukwangu chindanda chakwe (cha uchimwene) nkanaŵe kumbichilila ŵanganyao ali Asilamu?”"
  27,39,"Jwaŵechete jwamachili nnope mwa majini kuti: “Une chimbiche nacho kukwenu nkanin’jiime kutyoka pamalo penu (panganya jenu), soni chisimu une pa chalakwecho ndili jwamachili kusyene, soni jwakulupichika.”"
  27,40,"Jwaŵechete ajula juŵakwete umanyilisi wa m’chitabu kuti: “Une chinam’bichilile nacho nkaniliusyaausye kukwenu liso lyenu.” Basi ndema jajwachiweni (Sulaimana chindanda cha uchimwene chila) chili chitamilichiche kukwakwe jwatite: “Ayi ili mu ukoto wa Ambuje ŵangu kuti aninje yanti; ana tindogolele kapena tingane! Sano jwatatogolele nikuti akutogolela kwaalikamuchisya nsyene, nambo soni jwatakane basi (akukana kwaalikonya nsyene), chisimu Ambuje ŵangu ni Ŵakupata kwejinji (ŵangalajila chilichose), Ŵantuuka wannope.”"
  27,41,"(Sulaimana) jwatite: “Muntindanyichisye (kaoneche ka) chindanda chakwe (cha uchimwene), tulole kuti ana tachimanyilile kapena chaŵe mwa aŵala ŵangamanyilila (ichindu).”"
  27,42,"Basi ndema jaŵaiche (nyakongwe) yaŵechetedwe yanti: “Ana chindanda chenu (cha uchimwene) chikuŵa mpela achichi?” Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chikuŵa mpela nichichichi.” (Sulaimana jwatite): “Sano uwwe twapedwile umanyilisi nkanaŵe jwalakwe, soni twaŵele Asilamu.”"
  27,43,"Sano aila yajwaigalagatilaga kunneka Allah yansiŵililaga (nyakongwejo ku Usilamu), chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakuumila ku ŵandu achimakafili"
  27,44,"(Nyakongwe) ŵasalilidwe kuti: “Jinjilani mwipenu lyanyumba.” Basi ndema jaŵaliweni ŵaliganichisyaga kuti litanda, ni ŵakwindile (nguwo mpaka) kulosya sonjo syakwe. (Sulaimana) jwatite: “Chisimu lyalakwelitu lipenu lyanyumba lyesyasyajile ni magalasi.” (Nyakongwe) ŵatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu une naalitendele lupuso nansyene (paagalagatila inepe yangaŵaga Mmwe), sano nalipeleche pamo ni Sulaimana kwa Allah, M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope (ndili Nsilamu).”"
  27,45,"Soni chisimu chene Uwwe twatumisye kwa achina Samuda nnongo n’jao (jwali) Swaleh (juŵasalile kuti): “Mun’galagatilani Allah.” Basi naalole! Ŵanganyao ŵasyuchile kuŵa makuga gaŵili (lyakulupilila ni lyakanila) gagaliji nkukangana"
  27,46,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Ligongo chichi nkuijanguichisya yakusakala (kuti impate) nkaniiŵe yambone? Uli ngam’benda Allah chikuluko kuti ntendeledwe chanasa?”"
  27,47,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Uwwe tutapene ligongo lyenumwe ni ŵan’di namwe.” Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chitapani chenu chili kwa Allah (ligongo lya itendo yenu yangalumbana), nambo jenumanja ni ŵandu ŵankuliingwa (pakumpa yambone ni yakusakala).”"
  27,48,"Sano mu nsinda (wa Samuda) mwaliji mwana ŵandu nsano nancheche ŵaŵaliji nkuwatanganya pa chilambo, soni nganakolosyaga"
  27,49,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Nnumbililane kwa Allah kuti chisimu chitukampute ngondo chilo jwalakwe ni liŵasa lyakwe, kaneko chisimu chitunsalile jwawinjila jwakwe kuti: Uwwe nganituŵandika pa chonasiko cha liŵasa lyakwe, nambo soni chisimu uwwe tukuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  27,50,"Ni ŵapanjile malindi, nombe Uwwe nitwapanjile mipango jakonanga malindi gao kutendaga ŵanganyao akakumanyilila"
  27,51,Basi nnole mujaŵelele mbesi ja malindi gao! Chisimu Uwwe twajonasile ŵanganyao ni ŵandu ŵao wosopeŵene
  27,52,"Basi asila ni nyumba syao (syasyasyuchile kuŵa) mawuucha, ligongo lya lupuso lwao. Chisimu mu yalakwei mwana chilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵaakumanyilila"
  27,53,Ni twajokwele aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile nikuŵa ni woga (wakun’jogopa Allah)
  27,54,"Soni (munkumbuchilani) Lutwi pandema jaŵatite kwa ŵandu ŵakwe: “Ana nkuyiichilila yausakwa (matanyula) kutendaga jenumanja n’di nkuloleela?”"
  27,55,“Nambo yakuona jenumanja nkwaichilila achalume pakwanilisya isako yenu kwaleka achakongwe? Nambo jenumanja niŵandu ajinga.”